  "remarks": "Horizont Holding is a Belarusian holding company. Horizont Holding is one of the largest and most dynamically developing diversified holdings in the Republic of Belarus, covering a wide range of business areas. It has been described as one of the flagships of Minsk industry. Horizont Holding’s projects are being implemented with the instructions of Aliaksandr Lukashenka.",
